# Tech Stack

## Language & Runtime
- **Python 3.11+** managed with **uv** (package manager, venv, runner)
- Run everything via `uv run` or `make` targets

## Web Framework
- **FastAPI** with async endpoints, Pydantic v2 models
- **Uvicorn** as ASGI server
- **Jinja2** templates for server-side rendering (via `starlette.templating`)
- **HTMX** for dynamic interactions (loaded from CDN)
- **StaticFiles** for CSS/assets
- API prefix: `/api/v1`
- Web UI routes: `/` (search), `/chat`, `/documents`, `/documents/{id}`

## Database
- **PostgreSQL 16** via Docker (`pgvector/pgvector:pg16` image)
- **pgvector** extension for vector similarity search
- Host port **5433** (avoids default 5432 clashes)
- **SQLAlchemy 2.0** with async engine (`asyncpg`) for the API, sync engine (`psycopg2`) for CLI scripts
- No migration framework â€” `init_db()` uses `Base.metadata.create_all`; schema changes via raw ALTER TABLE

## AI / LLM
- **OpenAI SDK** (`openai` package)
- Embeddings: `text-embedding-3-small` (1536 dimensions)
- Chat: `gpt-4o-mini` with function/tool calling
- Tool calling used in CLI chatbot and web chat for RAG queries
- **Cohere** (`cohere` package) for reranking search results (`rerank-v3.5`)

## PDF Processing
- **pdf2image** (requires system `poppler`) â€” converts PDF pages to images
- **pytesseract** (requires system `tesseract`) â€” OCR on page images
- Two-step pipeline with per-step caching in `cache/{doc_id}/`

## Frontend
- **Jinja2 templates** in `templates/` directory
- **HTMX** for AJAX-like interactions without JavaScript framework
- **Vanilla JavaScript** for chat page (handles tool calling loop)
- **Static CSS** in `static/style.css`
- Single-process architecture â€” no separate frontend server

## Dev Tools
- **ruff** â€” formatting and linting
- **pyright** â€” type checking

## Key Config
- All settings via `pydantic-settings` (`app/config.py`), loaded from `.env`
- `DATABASE_URL`, `DATABASE_URL_SYNC`, `OPENAI_API_KEY` â€” required
- `COHERE_API_KEY` â€” required for reranking (search and chat)

## Make Targets
| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `make deps` | `uv sync` |
| `make dev` | Start FastAPI with hot reload |
| `make format` | ruff format + check --fix |
| `make typecheck` | pyright |
| `make db-up/down` | Docker Compose up/down |
| `make db-reset` | Reset DB schema, then migrate |
| `make migrate` | Create tables + pgvector extension |
| `make ingest` | Ingest PDFs from `example-pdfs/` (ROOT=, N= optional) |
| `make reingest` | Re-process documents (including finished) |
| `make prune` | Remove DB records for documents whose files no longer exist |
| `make enrich` | Enrich documents (memories, metadata) |
| `make reenrich` | Re-enrich documents (including finished) |
| `make chat` | Interactive CLI chatbot |
| `make generate-questions` | Generate test questions for search eval (N_QUESTIONS=10 per doc) |
| `make search-eval` | Run search eval over test questions (top_k=10, hit@1/2/4/8) |
